Package: otwfe
Type: Package
Title: Online Updating for Two-Way Fixed Effects Panel Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joonho", "Hwang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "joonhohwang@example.com")
Description: Algebraically exact online updating of two-way fixed effects (TWFE)
    panel regression estimators. Supports sequential updating of coefficients,
    classical variance, and cluster-robust variance (HC0, Arellano 1987) without
    revisiting historical data. Handles large CSV files via adaptive chunked
    reading. Based on Hwang & Lee (2026).
